            <section>
               <id root="083d2f8e-895b-4377-8be7-ef334af9e5a9"/>
               <code code="42229-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="SPL UNCLASSIFIED SECTION"/>
               <title>INGREDIENTS</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Each gram of Benzo-Jel™ 20% benzocaine gel contains between 180-220 mg benzocaine USP, in a water soluble base of PEG 3350 USP, PEG 400 USP, flavor, Sodium Saccharin USP, and FD&amp;C Red #40.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20150501"/>
            </section>
